title: HiddenOutsideOfSubscribeeCol
pid: 391b0816-592a-48dc-a5a2-0604c78a1663
body: |2-
  - set update
  - goal list is strange, but the name spells it out:
    each member is hidden by Col's grandparent and contained
    in none of Col's siblings (which are VoNodes)
  - children it creates, indefinitive, need no updating
  - lying members become independent
  - unusually, deletes itself if it finds itself empty
